'''''Ben & Ara''''', ni Filime yikinamico ya [[Kameruni]] iyobowe na Nnegest Likké ayikorana na Joseph Baird, Constance Ejuma, Q'orianka Kilcher, Matthew Norsworthy na Samone Norsworthy for Nursing Tybalt Productions, Wonder Worthy Productions na N- vision production<ref>https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/ben-ara-feature-film</ref><ref>https://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/dvd-ben-ara-joseph-baird/29949515</ref>. Filime izenguruka  abakandida 2 ba PhD, umwe w’umuyisilamu wo muri [[Afurika]] undi agnostic, aho batangira gukundana nyuma yo guhurira mu nzu ndangamurage ariko nyuma bakavumbura ko urukundo hagati yimico itandukanye n’amadini rushobora kugira ingaruka.<ref>https://mubi.com/films/ben-ara</ref><ref>http://africanwomenincinema.blogspot.com/2014/12/crowdfunding-ben-ara-film-directed-by.html</ref>  

Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Joseph Baird na Constance Ejuma mu nshingano zabo, hamwe na Akuyoe Graham, Q'orianka Kilcher, Michael Chieffo na William Mark McCullough mu nshingano zabo<ref>https://winterfilmawards.com/film/wfa16-ben-ara/</ref>.  Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi ndetse ikanerekanwa mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime<ref>https://winterfilmawards.com/film/wfa16-ben-ara/</ref>.     Yerekanwe bwa mbere muri Nzeri 2015 mu iserukiramuco rya Filimi ryigenga rya Miami. Muri 2016, film yatsindiye ibihembo byamafoto meza n’umukinnyi mwiza mu iserukiramuco rya Filime Indie<ref>http://africanwomenincinema.blogspot.com/2014/12/crowdfunding-ben-ara-film-directed-by.html</ref>.  Umukinnyi w'amafirime nyamukuru Constance Ejuma yatsindiye igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Nevada<ref>https://sime.nu/black-rifle-ioy/bc2fb4-ben-and-ara</ref>.  Muri 2016, iyi filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Filime nziza ya Diaspora muri African Movie Academy Awards (AMAA).<ref>http://www.spla.pro/file.person.nnegest-likke.18454.html</ref> 

